# Privacy Policy - Meme Lab Karma Casino

**Last Updated:** October 15, 2025

## 1. Introduction

This Privacy Policy explains how Meme Lab Karma Casino ("the App") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our Reddit Devvit application.

## 2. Information We Collect

### Automatically Collected Information
- **Reddit Username:** Your Reddit username is collected to identify you in the game
- **Game Data:** Karma Points balance, game statistics, meme creations, and leaderboard positions
- **Interaction Data:** Spin history, daily bonus claims, and game activity

### User-Provided Information
- **Meme Content:** Text and images you create using the meme generator
- **Game Choices:** Your selections and actions within the App

## 3. How We Use Your Information

We use collected information to:
- Provide and maintain the gaming experience
- Track your Karma Points and game progress
- Display leaderboards and statistics
- Prevent abuse and ensure fair gameplay
- Improve the App's features and performance

## 4. Data Storage

- All data is stored using Reddit's secure infrastructure (Redis)
- Data is associated with your Reddit username
- Game data persists across sessions within the subreddit
- We do not store data outside of Reddit's platform

## 5. Data Sharing

We do NOT:
- Sell your personal information
- Share your data with third parties
- Use your data for advertising
- Transfer data outside of Reddit's platform

Your game data IS visible to:
- Other users in the subreddit (leaderboards, public memes)
- Subreddit moderators (as part of Reddit's standard permissions)

## 6. Data Retention

- Game data is retained as long as the App is active in the subreddit
- Moderators may reset game data if needed
- If the App is removed from a subreddit, associated data may be deleted

## 7. Your Rights

You have the right to:
- Stop using the App at any time
- Request information about your stored data
- Contact subreddit moderators about data concerns
- Delete your Reddit account (which removes your data from the App)

## 8. Children's Privacy

The App is intended for users 13 years and older, consistent with Reddit's age requirements. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.

## 9. Security

We implement reasonable security measures:
- Data is stored securely using Reddit's infrastructure
- Access controls prevent unauthorized data access
- Rate limiting prevents abuse

However, no system is 100% secure. Use the App at your own risk.

## 10. Reddit's Privacy Policy

This App operates within Reddit's platform. Reddit's Privacy Policy also applies:
https://www.reddit.com/policies/privacy-policy

## 11. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy. Continued use of the App after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

## 12. Third-Party Services

The App uses:
- **Reddit Devvit Platform:** Subject to Reddit's privacy policies
- **Reddit API:** For user authentication and data storage

## 13. Contact Information

For privacy concerns or questions:
- Contact the app developer through Reddit
- Contact subreddit moderators where the App is installed
- Review Reddit's privacy resources

## 14. Compliance

This App complies with:
- Reddit's Developer Terms
- Reddit's Privacy Policy
- Applicable data protection regulations

---

By using Meme Lab Karma Casino, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy.
